1
00:00:05,338 --> 00:00:06,405
Does my cousin have some kind of beef

2
00:00:06,406 --> 00:00:07,439
with Lin Bingchen?

3
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,874
I'm not sure.

4
00:00:08,875 --> 00:00:09,975
But

5
00:00:09,976 --> 00:00:11,910
Bingchen seems to get

6
00:00:11,911 --> 00:00:13,191
really aggressive around Xiaoan.

7
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:15,647
Am I a threat to Hei Yan?

8
00:00:15,648 --> 00:00:17,049
Honestly,

9
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:18,685
I don't see how.

10
00:00:22,655 --> 00:00:24,991
Or does Hei Yan just dislike me?

11
00:00:25,759 --> 00:00:26,825
No, that's not it.

12
00:00:26,826 --> 00:00:28,194
We've never even worked together.

13
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:31,196
Could it be that he

14
00:00:31,197 --> 00:00:32,532
dumped him back in the day?

15
00:00:33,933 --> 00:00:35,968
I think you're overthinking it.

16
00:00:35,969 --> 00:00:36,803
Maybe he just

17
00:00:36,804 --> 00:00:38,238
doesn't want to deal with us.

18
00:00:39,172 --> 00:00:40,852
After all, you're just a performer to him.

19
00:00:42,575 --> 00:00:43,777
Hey, watch it!

20
00:00:52,252 --> 00:00:53,519
My sister is a huge fan of you both,

21
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,753
but she's too sick to be here.

22
00:00:54,754 --> 00:00:55,622
Could you two

23
00:00:55,622 --> 00:00:56,589
take a photo together

24
00:00:56,590 --> 00:00:57,623
to give her some strength?

25
00:00:57,624 --> 00:00:58,624
Sure thing.

26
00:00:59,092 --> 00:01:00,092
Let's take a photo.

27
00:01:01,227 --> 00:01:02,227
Thank you.

28
00:01:03,263 --> 00:01:04,630
She'll be so moved.

29
00:01:04,631 --> 00:01:06,032
She has chemo tomorrow.

30
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,133
Actually, let's record a video

31
00:01:08,134 --> 00:01:09,002
to cheer her up.

32
00:01:09,002 --> 00:01:09,669
Is that okay?

33
00:01:09,669 --> 00:01:10,336
Of course, of course.

34
00:01:10,337 --> 00:01:11,657
That's so kind of you. Thank you.

35
00:01:13,973 --> 00:01:17,210
I'm saying we should
do it for the girl in chemo.

36
00:01:19,179 --> 00:01:20,179
Ready?

37
00:01:21,948 --> 00:01:24,050
Hey, the world needs both black and white.

38
00:01:24,918 --> 00:01:25,718
Don't be like this guy,

39
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,019
always wearing a frown.

40
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:28,253
You should smile more!

41
00:01:28,254 --> 00:01:29,421
After the rain comes the sun.

42
00:01:29,422 --> 00:01:30,422
Hang in there!

43
00:01:31,658 --> 00:01:32,891
Thank you, Bai Xing.

44
00:01:32,892 --> 00:01:34,560
My sister is crying tears of joy.

45
00:01:34,561 --> 00:01:35,861
She hopes you and Hei Yan

46
00:01:35,862 --> 00:01:38,063
have huge hits with your new songs.

47
00:01:38,064 --> 00:01:39,732
She likes you both equally.

48
00:01:42,735 --> 00:01:44,203
Equally?

49
00:01:44,204 --> 00:01:46,172
There's always a favorite.

50
00:01:47,173 --> 00:01:48,173
Boss,

51
00:01:48,174 --> 00:01:49,508
it looks like people are actually shipping

52
00:01:49,509 --> 00:01:52,045
White Rice Cake and Black Forest.

53
00:01:52,345 --> 00:01:54,380
Send that to me. Now.

54
00:01:54,753 --> 00:01:57,423
You're not going to destroy them, are you?

55
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:01,054
In your eyes,

56
00:02:01,055 --> 00:02:02,388
do I really hate him that much?

57
00:02:02,789 --> 00:02:03,989
You always look grumpy.

58
00:02:03,990 --> 00:02:05,157
And when you're around Bai Xing,

59
00:02:05,158 --> 00:02:06,258
you get even stiffer.

60
00:02:06,259 --> 00:02:07,493
Some say you look down on him.

61
00:02:07,494 --> 00:02:08,927
Others say you're jealous.

62
00:02:08,928 --> 00:02:10,095
And then there are those who say

63
00:02:10,096 --> 00:02:11,096
your world isn't big enough

64
00:02:11,097 --> 00:02:12,999
for someone as talented as you.
